'''乳糖不耐'''（{{lang-en|Lactose Intolerance}}），又称'''乳糖消化不良'''或'''乳糖吸收不良'''，是有關[[乳糖|乳糖]]的[[食物不耐症|食物不耐症]]，乳糖常見於[[乳製品|乳製品]]中<ref name=NIH2014Dig/>。受乳糖不耐影響的人在症狀出現前可以耐受的乳糖量各不相同<ref name=NIH2014Dig/>。症狀可能包括[[腹痛|腹痛]]、[[腹脹|腹脹]]、[[腹瀉|腹瀉]]、[[屁|產氣]]及[[嘔吐|嘔吐]]<ref name=NIH2014Dig/>，這些通常在喝完牛奶後半小時到兩小時間開始發生<ref name=NIH2014Dig/>。嚴重度取決於一個人所吃或喝的量<ref name=NIH2014Dig>{{cite web|title=Lactose Intolerance|url=https://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/health-topics/digestive-diseases/lactose-intolerance/Pages/facts.aspx|website=NIDDK|access-date=25 October 2016|date=June 2014|deadurl=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161025111752/https://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/health-topics/digestive-diseases/lactose-intolerance/Pages/facts.aspx|archive-date=2016-10-25|df=}}</ref>。乳糖不耐本身不會破壞[[消化道|消化道]]<ref name=Heyman2006>{{cite journal | vauthors = Heyman MB | title = Lactose intolerance in infants, children, and adolescents | journal = Pediatrics | volume = 118 | issue = 3 | pages = 1279–86 | date = September 2006 | pmid = 16951027 | doi = 10.1542/peds.2006-1721 }}</ref>。

乳糖不耐是由於[[小腸|小腸]]中的[[乳糖酶|乳糖酶]]不足，因此無法將乳糖分解成[[葡萄糖|葡萄糖]]和[[半乳糖|半乳糖]]<ref name=Deng2015>{{cite journal | vauthors = Deng Y, Misselwitz B, Dai N, Fox M | title = Lactose Intolerance in Adults: Biological Mechanism and Dietary Management | journal = Nutrients | volume = 7 | issue = 9 | pages = 8020–35 | date = September 2015 | pmid = 26393648 | pmc = 4586575 | doi = 10.3390/nu7095380 | type = Review }}</ref>。有四種類型：原發性，繼發性，發育性和先天性。<ref name=NIH2014Dig/>原發性乳糖不耐症是指乳糖酶的量會隨著人們年齡增長而下降<ref name=NIH2014Dig/>。繼發性乳糖不耐症是由於小腸的損傷，例如感染，[[炎症性腸病|炎症性腸病]]或其他疾病<ref name=NIH2014Dig/><ref name=BerniCananiPezzella2016>{{cite journal | vauthors = Berni Canani R, Pezzella V, Amoroso A, Cozzolino T, Di Scala C, Passariello A | title = Diagnosing and Treating Intolerance to Carbohydrates in Children | journal = Nutrients | volume = 8 | issue = 3 | pages = 157 | date = March 2016 | pmid = 26978392 | pmc = 4808885 | doi = 10.3390/nu8030157 }}</ref>。發育性乳糖不耐症可能發生在[[早產兒|早產兒]]，而通常可在短時間內獲得改善<ref name=NIH2014Dig/> 。先天性乳糖不耐症是一種罕見的[[遺傳性疾病|遺傳性疾病]]，其中患者乳糖酶很少或根本沒有乳糖酶<ref name=NIH2014Dig/> 。

如果在飲食中消除乳糖後，就沒有對應症狀，則可以確認診斷。其他支持性測試包括{{le|氫氣呼吸測試|Hydrogen breath test}}和{{le|糞便酸度測試|Fecal pH test}}。可能產生類似症狀的其他疾病包括[[大腸激躁症|大腸激躁症]]，[[乳糜瀉|乳糜瀉]]和[[炎症性腸病|炎症性腸病]]。<ref name=NIH2014Dig/>乳糖不耐症不同於[[牛奶過敏|牛奶過敏]]<ref name=NIH2014Dig/>。處置方法通常是通過減少飲食中的乳糖量或服用乳糖酶補充劑<ref name=NIH2014Dig/>。乳糖不耐症患者人數未知<ref>{{cite web|title=How many people are affected or at risk for lactose intolerance?|url=https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/lactose/conditioninfo/Pages/risk.aspx|website=NICHD|access-date=25 October 2016|date=6 May 2014|deadurl=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161025112928/https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/lactose/conditioninfo/Pages/risk.aspx|archive-date=2016-10-25|df=}}</ref>。隨著年齡的增長，乳糖酶下降的人口百分比在北歐小於10%，在亞洲和非洲部分地區則高達95%<ref name=Deng2015/>。發病時間通常發生在兒童晚期或成年期<ref name=NIH2014Dig/>。根據目前資料，約在一萬年前，已經有部份人種發展出了在成年期時消化乳糖的能力<ref name=Deng2015/><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Ségurel L, Bon C | title = On the Evolution of Lactase Persistence in Humans | journal = Annual Review of Genomics and Human Genetics | volume = 18 | issue = 1 | pages = 297–319 | date = August 2017 | pmid = 28426286 | doi = 10.1146/annurev-genom-091416-035340 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Ingram CJ, Mulcare CA, Itan Y, Thomas MG, Swallow DM | title = Lactose digestion and the evolutionary genetics of lactase persistence | journal = Human Genetics | volume = 124 | issue = 6 | pages = 579–91 | date = January 2009 | pmid = 19034520 | doi = 10.1007/s00439-008-0593-6 }}</ref>。
